Here we are.

76
00:05:22,450 --> 00:05:22,890
Here.

77
00:05:39,330 --> 00:05:39,900
Thank you.

78
00:05:45,240 --> 00:05:46,620
Please take your seats.

79
00:05:47,940 --> 00:05:48,470
Okay.

80
00:05:56,750 --> 00:05:57,450
Kele, sit still.

81
00:06:01,430 --> 00:06:02,200
