Sure.

122
00:07:32,700 --> 00:07:33,130
Let's go.

123
00:07:35,340 --> 00:07:36,270
Come on.

124
00:07:38,700 --> 00:07:41,200
Let's go, Kele. Let's go have the cake.

125
00:07:42,680 --> 00:07:43,440
Wait.

126
